com.github.katjahahn

Class PEData

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.github.katjahahn.PEData

  • public class PEData
extends java.lang.Object
    Container that collects and holds the main information of a PE file. It is usually constructed by the PELoader and returned to the caller as result from scanning the PE File information.
